@VehicleService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5155
@BearerToken = <your-jwt-token-here>

### Health check (anonymous)
GET {{VehicleService_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a vehicle (Seller role required)
POST {{VehicleService_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "make": "Toyota",
  "model": "Corolla",
  "year": 2022,
  "vin": "1HGBH41JXMN109186",
  "price": 15000.00,
  "description": "Well maintained, single owner",
  "mileage": 45000,
  "fuelType": "Petrol",
  "transmission": "Automatic",
  "bodyType": "Sedan",
  "listingType": "ForSale",
  "color": "White",
  "country": "Morocco",
  "city": "Casablanca"
}

###

### Get all active vehicles (any authenticated user)
GET {{VehicleService_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get my vehicles (Seller role required)
GET {{VehicleService_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/my
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a vehicle by ID (any authenticated user)
GET {{VehicleService_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Update a vehicle (Seller role required)
PUT {{VehicleService_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 13500.00,
  "mileage": 48000,
  "description": "Price reduced, still in great shape"
}

###

### Update vehicle status (Seller role required)
PATCH {{VehicleService_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/status
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Active"
}

###

### Delete a vehicle (Seller role required)
DELETE {{VehicleService_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

###
